Package it.univr.passportease.helper.ratelimiter

Enum Class RateLimiter

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<RateLimiter>
it.univr.passportease.helper.ratelimiter.RateLimiter
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<RateLimiter>, Constable
public enum RateLimiter extends Enum<RateLimiter>
This enum contains all the rate limiters used in the application. Each enum value is associated with a Bandwidth object that represents the rate limiter. Every mutation or query that needs to be rate limited should be associated with a rate limiter.
